content: I kept getting Error 1002 trying to enable Usage Statistics. Then I turned off Wifi and I was able to enable everything. I never experienced that type of bug before....Hmmmm. Why?
replyContent: Hi Will, this issue seems to be specific to a security setting on a specific type of Wi-Fi router. The app only requires internet for setup and loading statistics. The exposure notification system does not require internet to function, so after set-up you can turn the Wi-Fi back on. We're working to fix this error now.
